<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>우리집 학교 포털</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./assets/css/styles.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <header class="topbar">
    <div class="brand">
      <div class="brand__title">우리집 학교 포털</div>
      <div class="brand__sub" id="brandSub">가족 전용</div>
    </div>
    <nav class="nav">
      <a href="#/notice" id="navNotice">공지</a>
      <a href="#/timetable" id="navTimetable">시간표</a>
      <a href="#/changes" id="navChanges">변동로그</a>
      <a href="#/admin" id="navAdmin" class="nav__muted">관리</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main class="container">
    <section class="searchbar" id="searchbar">
      <input id="q" type="search" placeholder="검색: 준비물 / 태권도 / 현장학습 / 돌봄…" />
      <button id="btnClear" class="btn btn--ghost">지우기</button>
    </section>

    <section id="view"></section>
  </main>

  <div class="modal" id="lockModal" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal__card">
      <h2>가족 전용</h2>
      <p class="muted" id="lockHint">공유 비밀번호를 입력하면 내용을 볼 수 있어요.</p>

      <label class="label">공유 비밀번호</label>
      <input id="sharedPass" type="password" autocomplete="current-password" />

      <label class="row mt8">
        <input id="remember" type="checkbox" />
        <span>이 기기에서 기억(권장하지 않음)</span>
      </label>

      <div class="row mt12">
        <button id="btnUnlock" class="btn">들어가기</button>
        <button id="btnGoSetup" class="btn btn--ghost">초기설정</button>
        <button id="btnReset" class="btn btn--ghost">초기화</button>
      </div>

      <div class="hint mt12">
        처음 1번은 <b>초기설정</b>에서 content.enc 파일을 만들어 업로드해야 합니다.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script type="module" src="./assets/js/app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
